contents: Move the scissors towards the space between the cassette and the knife~~~
Move the scissors halfway towards the space between the cassette and the knife~~~
Move the knife directly downward~~~
Move the soap to be directly above the knife~~~
Move the cassette to be directly above the soap~~~
Move the magnet away from the red candle and panda to be next to the yellowish candle~~~
Move the handcuffs one square closer to the yellowish candle, while keeping it in the same column~~~
Move the panda 1/3 of the way towards the yellowish candle~~~
Move the red candle down one square~~~
Move the airplane one square closer to the barrel, keeping it in the top row~~~
Move the sunglasses to be under the barrel, but in the same row as the saxophone~~~
Move the barrel to be directly above the sunglasses~~~
Move the barrel down so that it is above the sunglasses~~~ Do not move the sunglasses~~~
Move the saxophone up so it remains in the same column, but is in the same row as the barrel~~~
Move the binoculars so they are one square closer to the block but still in the bottom row~~~
Move the wrench to be directly next to the "A" block and in the top row~~~
Move the "B" block one square away from the edge while remaining in the same row~~~
Move the blue "B" block one square towards the binoculars, while keeping it in the same row~~~
Move the coffee cup one square so it is directly under the wrench~~~
Move the banana up one square~~~
Move the dollar to be directly under the banana~~~
Move the eraser up one square so it is in the same row as the dollar~~~
Move the feather to be directly under the eraser~~~
Move the carrot up one row to be in the same row as the measuring cup~~~
Move the measuring cup down one square~~~
Move the water bottle one square to be directly above the carrot~~~
Move the chair one square to be directly under the shot glass~~~
Move the comb up one square~~~
Move the mouse up one square~~~
